               <msContents>
                  <summary>The first volume of an incomplete set of the <title>Rawz̤at al-Ṣafā</title> (Garden of Purity), a general history from the creation of the world to the time of the author, together
                     with <ref target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_14609"
                        ><idno>Persian MS 174</idno></ref>, <ref
                           target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_14610">175</ref>, <ref
                              target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_6657">176</ref>, 
                     <ref target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_6658">177</ref>, and <ref
                        target="https://www.fihrist.org.uk/catalog/manuscript_6659">178</ref>. However, the set lacks the fourth volume and a geographical appendix often added as the eighth, hence only six total. 
                     While nearly uniformly bound, the different formats and colophons within the set indicate completion in different locations and times.</summary>
                  <msItem xml:id="Persian_MS_173-item1"> 
                     <author key="person_175393012" ref="http://viaf.org/viaf/175393012/" change="#ids-cleanup">
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="standard">Mīr Khvānd, Muḥammad ibn Khāvandshāh, 1433-1498</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa">مير خواند، محمد بن خواندشاه</persName>
                     </author>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="work_273" change="#ids-cleanup">Rawz̤at al-Ṣafā fī Sīrat al-Anbiyā wa-al-Mulūk</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" type="alt" key="work_273">Rawz̤at al-Ṣafā</title>
                     <title xml:lang="fa" key="work_273" change="#ids-cleanup">روضة الصفاء فی سیرة الانبيا و الملوك</title>
                     <incipit xml:lang="ar" type="basmallah"><locus from="1b" to="1b"> برگ ۱پ (folio 1b):</locus>
                        زی‍ب‌ ف‍ه‍رس‍ت‌ ن‍س‍خ‍ه‌ م‍ف‍اخ‍ر ان‍ب‍ی‍ا ع‍ال‍ی‍م‍ک‍ان‌ و زی‍ن‍ت‌ دی‍ب‍اچ‍ه‌ م‍ج‍م‍وع‍ه‌ م‍اث‍ر س‍لاطی‍ن‌. </incipit>
                     <explicit xml:lang="fa">
                        <locus from="388b" to="388b"> برگ ۳۸۸پ (folio 388b):
                        </locus> علی مالیاء قدیر و بالرجبات حدیر و السلام علی خمسه ابیع اللهی (؟). </explicit>
                     <colophon xml:lang="fa">
                        <locus from="388b" to="388b"> برگ ۳۸۸پ (folio 388b):</locus>
                     تمام شد جلد اول روضة الصفا بتاریخ بیست و چهارم شوال سنة ۱۲۱۸ هجری نبوی 
                            </colophon>
                     <colophon>Completed on <date
                           calendar="#Hijri-qamari" when="1804-02-06">24 Shavvāl 1218 AH (6 Feb. 1804 CE)</date>.</colophon>
                     <textLang mainLang="fa">Persian</textLang>
                  </msItem>
